data.description: 3 bedroom, 1-bathroom acreage located on a hard surfaced road on 2.94 acres. Numerous updates through the years which include but not limited to: Siding, Windows, flooring, Roof (2020) and bathroom updated.  This acreage is in a good location, 5 minutes from I-35 , 20 minutes from Iowa Falls and 15 minutes from Hampton.  5 minutes from Latimer and Coulter.  Call us today to schedule a showing.  Sellers will NOT consider a contract sale.
